    <h3 class="!mt-6 link--theme">Summary:</h3>
    <p>
      "Daring Greatly" by Brené Brown explores the power of vulnerability and
      courage in fostering meaningful connections and personal growth. Brown's
      research-backed insights inspire readers to embrace vulnerability as a
      pathway to authenticity and wholehearted living.
    </p>

    <h3 class="link--theme">What It Teaches:</h3>
    <p>
      "Daring Greatly" by Brené Brown teaches readers the importance of
      embracing vulnerability as a source of strength, fostering authentic
      connections, and cultivating courage to overcome shame and fear. It
      provides practical strategies for daring to be vulnerable and living a
      more fulfilling, wholehearted life.
    </p>

    <h3 class="link--theme">Amazon Review:</h3>
    <p class="text-sm">
      "This book put into words feelings and experiences that I have had my
      whole life and could never quite put my finger on. Everyone needs to read
